{"tid":1680911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個沒有人民授權的法院，是否應該推翻佢","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:45:37.000Z","uid":124410,"like":18,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"29ed0a6c975aaa12141e49c583c493b901c50714","tid":1680911,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？"},{"pid":"aa21c65f6ff6e9ddc5f1b8505f1d39f77392694c","tid":1680911,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"18e9fd9a4643d0524c5b0a3987eedde20b2170df","tid":1680911,"uid":136893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"8e3d0a60b5317d972747a91c6e623af70968cc7d","tid":1680911,"uid":235025,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dbd0d72e42e1b6e383f54026168fe5828fc2d15","tid":1680911,"uid":51546,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔：有法院就有法治<br />\n法官判拉晒d示威者者<br />\n連登仔：法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f376d1ce5f3f4fe38ee1452d42703d3aad1fdc66","tid":1680911,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"a95a564b2eb4fa03106671cd058c70cdb8b9a1ff","tid":1680911,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:07:44.000Z","msg":"冇人民授權既政府委任既法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665f848cb28d2438cde004efef95eb331f79e1f3","tid":1680911,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔：法院 = 法治<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔明, 係支那及殖民地「三權合作」之下<br />\n<br />\n香港法院同北韓法院係無分別<br />\n<br />\n只係裝裝門面而已 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9729a2e3be5d70a489996d4dde25e49f88e3242d","tid":1680911,"uid":28831,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"665f848cb28d2438cde004efef95eb331f79e1f3","tid":1680911,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔：法院 = 法治<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔明, 係支那及殖民地「三權合作」之下<br />\n<br />\n香港法院同北韓法院係無分別<br />\n<br />\n只係裝裝門面而已 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:09:46.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n以胸襲警都入到個下已經要解散法院<br />\n根本香港既法院就唔係法治象徵<br />\n有人去搞法院我都唔會割"},{"pid":"aca6108e0d9cc8de7b3ec31a35f9a04e50ca0947","tid":1680911,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:12:02.000Z","msg":"一個冇人民認同的法院就應該推翻佢<br />\n認同係比授權重要<br />\n民主國家都有授權法官審判的權力<br />\n但一旦法官的審判審判得唔到人民的認同<br />\n人民就應該收回法庭的權力 推翻法庭<br />\n<br />\n以前香港的法院都冇人民授權<br />\n但人民認同／接受法庭的判決<br />\n法庭的判決同人民的期望接近一致 偏差唔會太大<br />\n所以人民唔會推翻法庭"},{"pid":"42d14a3113911a639e96589c0b7bad1f4482dbff","tid":1680911,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"應該引入民選法官制度"},{"pid":"74f150293b30abfc28d37b9d7173e8e4781bba54","tid":1680911,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n但具體行動係點要傾"},{"p